text: Nebočaj is a village in Vogošća municipality, near Sarajevo, Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina, Bosnia and Herzegovina. ==Population== ===Ethnic composition, 1991 census=== total: 465 * Serbs - 356 (76.55%) * Muslims by nationality - 94 (20.21%) * "Yugoslavs" - 13 (2.79%) * others and unknown - 2 (0.43%) ==History== ==References== * Official results from the book: Ethnic composition of Bosnia-Herzegovina population, by municipalities and settlements, 1991. census, Zavod za statistiku Bosne i Hercegovine - Bilten no.234, Sarajevo 1991. title: Nebočaj
